image - Variable in class assets.Sprite
Image of the sprite
imageList - Variable in class assets.Player
ArrayList containing all other ArrayLists with frames of animation of the player.
initBackground(int) - Method in class assets.Background
Loads image of background from resources and gets it's dimensions.
initBullet() - Method in class assets.Bullet
Loads image of the bullet from resources and gets it's dimensions.
initCoin() - Method in class assets.Coin
Loads image of the coin from resources and gets it's dimensions.
initDanger() - Method in class assets.Danger
Loads image of the danger sign from resources and gets it's dimensions.
initGame() - Method in class game.Game
This method initializes the game for the first time when it's started.
initHeart(boolean) - Method in class assets.Heart
Loads image of heart or shield(if bought) from resources and gets it's dimensions.
initLives() - Method in class game.Game
This method is used while creating new game objects to create 3 Heart objects(or 4 if user bought a shield in the shop) and add them do sprites ArrayList
initMusic() - Method in class assets.Music
Finds audio file based on Game.musicOption and loads it to Music.backgroundMusic.
initPlayer() - Method in class assets.Player
Loads images from resources folder and adds them to appropriate ArrayLists and ads those list to imageList array.
initPowerup(int) - Method in class assets.Powerup
Loads image of powerup from resources and gets it's dimensions.
initShooter() - Method in class assets.Shooter
Loads images from resources folder and adds them to Shooter.shooterRun.
initSounds() - Method in class assets.Sound
Loads audio files based on Game.musicOption.
initSpike(int) - Method in class assets.Obstacle
Loads image of obstacle from resources and gets it's dimensions.
initTimers() - Method in class game.Game
This method sets levelTime based on level selected by the user and creates random numbers for all random timers.
initWindow() - Method in class game.Start
This method initializes Game class, blocks option to change size of the program's window by the user, sets size of the window based on static values in Game class:Game.windowWidth and Game.windowHeight, sets the name of the application that will be displayed at top of the window, sets the window to always start at the center of the screen and enables the option to close the application by pressing X in top right corner.
isVisible() - Method in class assets.Sprite
Gets visible boolean
item - Variable in class menus.ShopButton
First item is the initiative item (before being selected)
